                <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-8">
                    <h2>Redon Skikuli</h2>
                    <h3>Open Labs Hackerspace</h3>
                    <p>A hacktivist, open knowledge/culture promoter located in the Balkans area. In 2012 co-founded Open Labs Hackersace, the Tirana based community promoting the idea of free open source technologies, the concept of the commons, copyright reform in the digital age and open data.
A Mozilla Representative for Albania, co-organizer of OSCAL, Wikipedia Weekend & Mozilla Weekend. Redon is also an OpenStreetMap editor, a Wikimedian and initiator of Wiki Loves Maps & Wiki Loves Audio projects.</p>
